{"title":"写在大字报前","authors":["李学鳌"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":9,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"写在大字报前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李学鳌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写在大字报前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像孔雀展屏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像百花齐放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红红绿绿的大字报啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴满路旁的墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精粹的语言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明确的思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在大字报前观看、行走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像游泳在智慧的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整风是一面明镜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嵌在社会主义的关上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能否过得关去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请在镜前检查、衡量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上有灰尘必须洗掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切莫姑息、掩藏！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淳朴的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚穿布便鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身穿蓝衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人群里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他淳朴得像老师傅一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人们爱向他说心里话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他从心里更爱读工人们的文章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当他离开工厂的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们才知他是中央来的首长。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}